{
  "name": "Comment",
  "summary": "<p><strong>Comment</strong> 对象是 <strong>Comments</strong> 集合的成员。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong>Comment</strong> 属性可返回 <strong>Comment</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例更改单元格 E5 中的批注文本。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comment</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Text</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;reviewed on &quot;</span> + <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Date</span>())\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>使用 <strong>Comments</strong>(<em>index</em>)（其中 <em>index</em> 为批注号）可返回 <strong>Comments</strong> 集合中的单条批注。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例隐藏第一张工作表中的第二条批注。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comments</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>使用 <strong>AddComment</strong> 方法可在区域内添加批注。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表的单元格 E5 中添加批注。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myComment = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddComment</span>()\n    myComment.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    myComment.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Text</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;reviewed on &quot;</span> + <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Date</span>())\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表单元格批注。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a>**对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>){\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n\t\t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n\t}\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n\t\t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n\t}\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Author",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置批注的作者。<strong>String</strong> 类型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除活动工作表中由 Jean Selva 添加的所有批注。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myComments = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comments</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> c = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; c &lt;= myComments.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; c++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (myComments.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(c).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Author</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Jean Selva&quot;</span>) {\n            myComments.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(c).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表中 D5 单元格中批注的作者。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comment</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Author</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Shape",
      "summary": "<p>确保批注未被隐藏。在“ 审阅 ”选项卡上，选择“ 批注&gt;显示所有批注”。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Shape/Shape .htm#Shape.Shape\">Shape</a>**对象，它代表连接到指定批注的形状。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例选定活动工作表上的第二条批注。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comments</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shape</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上第三条批注的形状的宽度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comments</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shape</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Width</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Shape",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Visible",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Boolean</strong> 值，它确定对象是否可见。可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例隐藏单元格 A2 中的批注。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comment</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 A4 单元格的批注是否可见。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comment</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Delete",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>删除对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除 A1 单元格的批注。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comment</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例遍历活动工作表上所有批注，并删除该工作表中由 jack 添加的所有批注。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> comments = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comments</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> c = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; c &lt;= comments.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; c++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (comments.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(c).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Author</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;jack&quot;</span>) {\n            comments.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(c).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "Next",
      "summary": "<p>本方法仅对单张工作表有效。对工作表中最后一条批注使用本方法可返回 <strong>Null</strong>（不是下一张工作表的第一条批注）。</p>\n<p>在没有现有注释的新工作簿中测试此示例。 若要清除工作簿中的所有批注，请在“即时”窗格中使用 Selection.SpecialCells(xlCellTypeComments).Delete() 。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Comment/Comment .htm#Comment.Comment\">Comment</a></strong> 对象，该对象代表下一条批注。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例隐藏下一条批注。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//Sets up the comments</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xNum = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; xNum &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>; xNum++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A&quot;</span> + xNum).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddComment</span>()\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A&quot;</span> + xNum).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comment</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Text</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Comment &quot;</span> + xNum)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Comments created... A1:A10&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//Deletes every second comment in the A1:A10 range</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> yNum = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; yNum &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>; yNum = yNum + <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A&quot;</span> + yNum).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comment</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Next</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shape</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Deleted every second comment&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 A3 单元格下一条批注的内容。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comment</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Next</span>().<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Text</span>())\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "<p>Comment</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "name": "Previous",
      "summary": "<p>本方法仅对单张工作表有效。对工作表中第一条批注使用本方法可返回 <strong>Null</strong>（不是前一张工作表的最后一条批注）。</p>\n<p>在没有现有注释的新工作簿中测试此示例。 若要清除工作簿中的所有批注，请在“即时”窗格中使用 Selection.SpecialCells(xlCellTypeComments).Delete() 。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Comment/Comment .htm#Comment.Comment\">Comment</a></strong> 对象，该对象代表前一条批注。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例使用 Previous 方法导航，每隔一条删除评论。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//Sets up the comments</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xNum = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; xNum &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>; xNum++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A&quot;</span> + xNum).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddComment</span>()\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A&quot;</span> + xNum).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comment</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Text</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Comment &quot;</span> + xNum)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Comments created... A1:A10&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//Deletes every second comment in the A1:A10 range</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> yNum = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>; yNum &gt;= <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; yNum = yNum - <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A&quot;</span> + yNum).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comment</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Previous</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shape</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Deleted every second comment&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 A4 单元格上一条批注的内容。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comment</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Previous</span>().<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Text</span>())\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "<p>Comment</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "name": "Text",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>设置批注文本。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将 A2 单元格的批注文本设置为&quot;这是一个批注&quot;。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comment</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Text</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;这是一个批注&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在 A4 单元格的批注内容中第三个字符开始插入“hello”，并显示结果。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comment</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Text</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;hello&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Text",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>要添加的文本。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "Start",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>所添加文本的起始位置（字符数）。如果省略此参数，则删除批注中的所有现有文字。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "Overwrite",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>如果为 True，则覆盖现有文本。默认值是 False（插入文本）。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        }
      ],
      "returns": "<p>String</p>\n"
    }
  ]
}